songs.title: Molly Fun Ride
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
ChaseTheMoney

[Hook]
I got raw molly, I got all molly (all molly)
I got raw molly, I got all molly (all molly)
Molly fun ride, molly fun ride (fun ride)
Molly fun ride, molly fun ride (fun ride)

[Post-Hook]
Check my phone ring, check my phone ring (check my phone ring)
See my phone ring, see my phone ring (see my phone ring)
See my phone ring, see my phone ring (see my phone ring)
See my phone ring, see my phone ring (see my phone ring)

[Verse]
See my bad bitch, see my bad bitch
Got a bad bitch, above average
See my phone ring, from a bad bitch
In a two door, not a four door (no)
In a new ho, not a old ho
I got your ho, you can have her
I don’t want her, you can have her
All I want is guap, all I want is guap

[Hook]
I got raw molly, I got all molly (all molly)
I got raw molly, I got all molly (all molly)
Molly fun ride, molly fun ride (fun ride)
Molly fun ride, molly fun ride (fun ride)

[Post-Hook]
Check my phone ring, check my phone ring (check my phone ring)
See my phone ring, see my phone ring (see my phone ring)
See my phone ring, see my phone ring (see my phone ring)
See my phone ring, see my phone ring (see my phone ring)
